(a ∷ ε) ∈? (literal b) = no (λ ())
(b ∷ ε) ∈? (literal a) = no (λ ())
(b ∷ ε) ∈? (literal b) = yes ∈literal
(w₁ ∷ (w₂ ∷ ws)) ∈? (literal x) = no (λ ())

w ∈? (r₁ + r₂) with w ∈? r₁ | w ∈? r₂
...| yes t₁ | yes  t₂ = yes (∈+ˡ t₁)
...| yes t₁ | no t₂ = yes (∈+ˡ t₁)
...| no t₁ | yes t₂ = yes (∈+ʳ t₂)
...| no t₁ | no t₂ = no (λ x → ⊻ t₁ t₂ x)

